"{\"uid\": \"horseandhound.co.uk-news-aistis-vitkauskas-olympic-place-lost-863669\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"A Lithuanian eventer has spoken of his disappointment at losing his individual place at theParis Olympicsafter he did not gain his final qualification when he was eliminated atLuhm\\u00fchlen Horse Trials (13-16 June).\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A Lithuanian eventer\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 20}, {\"ngram\": \"his disappointment\", \"from\": 35, \"to\": 53}, {\"ngram\": \"his individual place\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 84}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympicsafter\", \"from\": 88, \"to\": 110}, {\"ngram\": \"his final qualification\", \"from\": 127, \"to\": 150}, {\"ngram\": \"atLuhm\\u00fchlen Horse Trials\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 198}, {\"ngram\": \"13-16 June\", \"from\": 200, \"to\": 210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aistis Vitkauskas was due to ride as an individual at Paris, having gained a place as one of the two highest-ranked athletes fromFEIgroup C (central and Eastern Europe, central Asia).\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 268, \"end\": 273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999936353108, \"rank\": 6.364673894442853e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aistis Vitkauskas\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 231}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 264}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 296}, {\"ngram\": \"the two highest-ranked athletes\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 338}, {\"ngram\": \"fromFEIgroup C\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 353}, {\"ngram\": \"central and Eastern Europe\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"central Asia\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aistis and 13-year-old gelding Commander Vg were competing in the Luhm\\u00fchlen CCI5*, where they were trying to obtain their final Olympic minimum eligibility requirement (MER) before the 24 June deadline.\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 570, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manx_Electric_Railway\", \"score\": 0.9999963718653241, \"rank\": 3.627856032558023e-06, \"text\": \"MER\", \"types\": [\"Q728937\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manx_Electric_Railway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manx_Electric_Railway\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aistis\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"gelding Commander Vg\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 444}, {\"ngram\": \"the Luhm\\u00fchlen CCI5\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"their final Olympic minimum eligibility requirement\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"the 24 June deadline\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But they were eliminated across country under the dangerous riding rule; they were stopped by a fence judge shortly after jumping fence 10abc; an upright to a ditch, then a skinny flower box.\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"the dangerous riding rule\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"a fence judge\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"fence 10abc\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"a ditch\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aistis toldH&Htheir warm-up, in dry conditions, \\\"went well\\\", then it started raining heavily before they left the start box.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aistis toldH&Htheir warm-up\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"dry conditions\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"the start box\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said that at fence 10a Commander Vg lifted well with his front legs but as they were jumping the gelding looked at the ditch causing him to \\\"freeze\\\" momentarily and not lift his back legs fully.\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fence 10a Commander Vg\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"his front legs\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"the gelding\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"the ditch\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"his back legs\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1116}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Commander Vg made contact with the fence, but the MIM clip was not activated, and they cleared elements b and c. \\\"When they stopped me I could not understand why and thought it must have been because someone had fallen in front of me.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Online_Mendelian_Inheritance_in_Man\", \"score\": 0.9960599964920495, \"rank\": 0.003955588540022518, \"text\": \"MIM\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Online_Mendelian_Inheritance_in_Man\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Online_Mendelian_Inheritance_in_Man\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Commander Vg\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"the fence\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1164}, {\"ngram\": \"elements\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"b\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1229}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I was told I must leave the track I was very confused,\\\" said Aistis, who went to see the ground jury.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"Aistis\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1432}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground jury\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The ground jury president said, 'We know that you and Commander normally do much better, and this is not your day.'\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ground jury president\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"Commander\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"your day\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was told I'd been stopped for dangerous riding at fence 10abc.\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dangerous riding\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"fence 10abc\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I argued that in my opinion the fence was very well handled by the horse, it was a tough moment, but it was the opposite to dangerous riding.\\\"\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my opinion\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"the fence\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1722}, {\"ngram\": \"a tough moment\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"the opposite\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"dangerous riding\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aistis, who believes the ground jury made the wrong decision, said he was then told that his jump at fence 5abc fell under the same dangerous riding criteria.\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aistis\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground jury\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrong decision\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1854}, {\"ngram\": \"his jump\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"fence\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"5abc\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"the same dangerous riding criteria\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That completely blew me off; I had a bad line but I did not have a bad jump.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bad line\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"a bad jump\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ground jury stopped discussing it with me and said that it was done,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ground jury\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aisitis received an official FEI warning for dangerous riding.\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2145, \"end\": 2148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.78319289602586e-38, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aisitis\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"dangerous riding\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said the Lithuanian federation asked the FEI if he and Commander Vg could compete in Strzegom, Poland, (20-23 June) the week after Luhm\\u00fchlen to try to gain their MER for Paris, but were told they could not.\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2191, \"end\": 2201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuanian_language\", \"score\": 0.7444585374654262, \"rank\": 0.33693375100536305, \"text\": \"Lithuanian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuanian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2223, \"end\": 2226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.78319289602586e-38, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Spo